snippet.title: ScreenSlam
snippet.description:
We are an Entertainment channel that features Hollywood interviews, premieres, behind the scenes of movies & TV, press conferences, award shows, film festivals, and much more. Our content is made up of original videos and stuff that the studios send us. We edited our videos so you can check out the latest movies and streaming shows in a quick, entertaining fashion.

- The ScreenSlam Team
